title: Lunchbox Wants To Scalp ‘Tickets’ To Bobby’s Wedding + Nick Offerman Shares 'Parks + Rec' Stories + Our 'One Has To Go' Game!
itunes:title: Lunchbox Wants To Scalp ‘Tickets’ To Bobby’s Wedding + Nick Offerman Shares 'Parks + Rec' Stories + Our 'One Has To Go' Game!
description:
Lunchbox shares his idea for inviting listeners to Bobby’s wedding for a price. We talk to Nick Offerman (who played Ron Swanson on Parks and Rec) about working with famous funny people, his new show and his favorite memories from that show. We played another round of the “One Has To Go” game that is very controversial.
